{"tid":1149814,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"廠迷唔想細梅踢決賽：收埋佢本護照！","createTime":"2019-05-11T11:47:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-11T14:54:18.000Z","uid":199590,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9caf7e8761707b017970e46c8ffddcdc006668bb","tid":1149814,"uid":199590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T11:47:08.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】阿仙奴球迷極不願意看到中堅梅斯達菲於歐霸盃決賽披甲，更於網上跪求有人收起他的護照！<br />\n<br />\n在阿仙奴的防線之中，以身為德國2014年世界盃冠軍功臣梅斯達菲（Shkodran Mustafi）的名氣最大，但今季表現不濟，經常「派膠」導致失球，成為計時炸彈。<br />\n<br />\n一眾廠迷都不希望於歐霸盃決賽看到梅斯達菲的身影，紛紛在Twitter發表意見。有人說：「我們從未如此需要一名領袖，有人要挺身而出，在決賽前收起梅斯達菲的護照。」有人則表示：「請把梅斯達菲、艾尼利留在倫敦。」更有人指：「踢10個比有梅斯達菲在陣時踢11個更好。」<br />\n<br />\n兵工廠於歐霸盃4強次回合，在梅斯達菲僅後備入替的情況下，作客以4:2擊敗華倫西亞，兩回合合計大勝7:3，殺入5月29日於阿塞拜疆首都巴庫舉行的決賽，惡戰同樣來自英超的車路士。"},{"pid":"b3089cad3acfa53696e5440e281c2b23fe45411c","tid":1149814,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T12:26:50.000Z","msg":"比米希達恩果本佢"},{"pid":"74087e58ae5fe48b03993c02cff908171694f652","tid":1149814,"uid":131369,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T12:28:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/03/083456_5008241d15cc131843edd3ecaa1fc7a4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F03%2F083456_5008241d15cc131843edd3ecaa1fc7a4.jpg&h=95748211&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"03939165edebf4736d53b669afe409e479549bb6","tid":1149814,"uid":119778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74087e58ae5fe48b03993c02cff908171694f652","tid":1149814,"uid":131369,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T12:28:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/03/083456_5008241d15cc131843edd3ecaa1fc7a4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F03%2F083456_5008241d15cc131843edd3ecaa1fc7a4.jpg&h=95748211&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-